OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who gambled away a huge Covid-19 
OL,6, relief handout after receiving the     
OL,7, money mistakenly says he will pay      
OL,8, Japanese authorities back "bit by bit",
OL,9, according to local media.              
OL,11,FThe man was mistakenly sent 46.3m yen  
OL,12,F($357,400; #287,000) in April which was
OL,13,Fsupposed to be shared among 463 people 
OL,14,Fin a town in western Japan.            
OL,16,F"I feel very sorry that I used it up," 
OL,17,Fthe man said according to his lawyer.  
OL,19,FThe southern town of Abu is suing the  
OL,20,Fman and is considering criminal action.
